<h2 class="bold font-l">Chirrut Imwe</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Chirrut is blind and has no trouble wiping out a platoon of Stormtroopers with only his staff. </p>
<p class='example_row'>Example of:<br><a href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/BlindWeaponmaster" class='trope-example-link'>Blind Weaponmaster</a></p>
</div>
